To all those having issues with the file being "password protected," check your .rar handling client or clean your computer - the file is good.

However, I do not see the point in submitting a torrent in .rar format.  Is it hard to extract the file or watch from within?  No.  Is it annoying?  Slightly.  The compression saves minimal disk space at best.

That being said, I got rid of cable 2 years ago, and I watch all of my TV online thanks to uploaders like this.
